      <div class="stat-label">University Placement</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="journey-section">
  <div class="journey-container">
    <div class="journey-text">
      <span class="section-tag">Our Journey</span>
      <h2>From Humble Beginnings to <span class="highlight">Educational Excellence</span></h2>
      <p>Founded in 2012, KingsField Academy started with just 45 students and a vision to revolutionize education in Edo State. Today, we stand proud as one of Benin City's most respected educational institutions.</p>
      <p>Our commitment to blending traditional values with modern teaching methodologies has created a unique learning environment where every child discovers their potential and develops the confidence to pursue their dreams.</p>
      
      <div class="milestones">
        <div class="milestone">
          <div class="milestone-year">2012</div>
          <div class="milestone-text">Founded with 45 students</div>
        </div>
        <div class="milestone">
          <div class="milestone-year">2015</div>
          <div class="milestone-text">First WAEC cohort - 100% pass rate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="milestone">
          <div class="milestone-year">2018</div>
          <div class="milestone-text">Opened state-of-the-art science lab</div>
        </div>
        <div class="milestone">
          <div class="milestone-year">2024</div>
          <div class="milestone-text">Recognized as top private school in Benin</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="journey-image">
      <img src="/Images/logo.jpg" alt="KingsField Academy Campus" loading="lazy">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

